features: ESSENTIAL STORAGE BASKET FOR NEWBORN PRODUCTS - The Parker Baby Diaper Caddy (patented) is versatile enough for all that baby stuff: baby toys, diapers, baby clothes, baby wipes, bibs, onesies, cloth diapers, changing pads, medicine, burp cloths and other baby essentials! Large enough for dozens of diapers and most wipes dispensers.

REMOVABLE ORGANIZER INSERT - Remove the diaper organizer insert to use as a toy storage bin, baby hamper or nursery basket for additional nursery storage. Our lightweight, portable diaper caddy is 13 x 9 x 7" (Regular Size) and made of soft felt and features sturdy outer pockets for additional baby storage.

DESIGNED TO COMPLIMENT YOUR NURSERY DECOR - Our diaper caddy basket is designed with neutral white color to look good in any room. It looks good on your changing table, on top of a dresser or next to the diaper pail and is an essential item for your diaper changing station. Easily move the tote around using the long handle.

MULTI PURPOSE KIT - With multiple compartments, you can easily store all of your breast pump and breast pump parts, use as a car organizer, store all those bath products or place bedside to make things easier to find during those late night feedings.
THOUGHTFUL BABY SHOWER IDEA - The Parker Baby Diaper Caddy is a practical gift and should be on every baby registry. It makes for a great baby gift!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A must have! I buy for every baby shower.
reviews.reviewText: The Parker Baby Diaper Caddy has proven to be an essential and stylish addition to my nursery and all of my mom friends. Its large size offers ample storage space for diapers, wipes, and other baby essentials, promoting easy organization. The sturdy and lightweight design allows for convenient portability, making it a versatile storage solution at home or in the car. The neutral white color complements any nursery decor, and the quality materials ensure durability. Overall, a practical and aesthetically pleasing choice for keeping baby supplies tidy and accessible.Although my daughter is now grown, I still purchase for all my new mom friends. We now use ours for a snack and book caddy in the car.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I know it’s something simple, but it’s perfect!! I didn’t expect to love this diaper caddy so much! My fifth baby boy will be here in less than 8 weeks and I wanted something cute, simple, stylish, and aesthetically appealing. It’s all these and more! Great price for great quality. Not too big, plenty of compartments. Love the gray that I chose, as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is one of the best carryall I've seen. It's a neutral color, lightweight material with tons of pockets and storage area with dividers. Keeps all your stuff organized. Easy to transport from room to room or in the car. Very happy with this purchase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for what I needed!
reviews.reviewText: We have been going over a year now with diapers and creams piled up on the dresser and finally I had to do something about it. I found this product and liked the rectangular shape and it had a lot of pockets around the side of it. It works perfect in our space and I feel so much more organized! Quality was good for us and we got the product quickly!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 3, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I received one of these as a gift off of my baby registry and I bought another because I liked it so much. I'm using one as a diaper caddy and the other to hold my breast pump/accessories. I like all the pockets and that you have flexibility in how many compartments you want on the inside. I'm not sure how well it will hold up, but it does look nice and seems well made.

reviews.reviewTitle: Genial para poner estaciones de cambio en casa o automóvil
reviews.reviewText: Me gusta que las asas son resistentes y que fácilmente puedes llevártelo a cualquier otra recámara u área de la casa (especialmente útil si tienes casa grande o de 2 pisos) o al automóvil para tener todo lo que necesites para tu bebé a la mano.Ayuda a estar organizada y con estilo. Buena opción para viajar con bebé en automóvil.Me hubiera gustado que el color estuviera disponible en un tono más obscuro para evitar que se ensucie, aún así se puede lavar sin problema.

The caddy is beautifully made and looks great. I use it as an organiser in my car - I keep it on the passenger seat and keep my lunch, makeup bag, tissues etc in it, then bring it all in to the house when I get home. And on long car trips my 5 year old has it next to her in the back seat - with drawing book, textas, lunch box, drink bottle, tissues. It is SO useful and looks beautiful. It is really robust. Highly recommended!
Thanks I received the item and was pleased with it.
